  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ProvisioningHandler
    A ProvisioningHandler defines the service API to be implemented by service providers extending the provisioning mechanism.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ProvisioningProperties
    The ProvisioningProperties is an utility class to read a properties file containing data for automatic provisioning.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ProvisioningException
    Exception which should be thrown if provisioning fails for some reason.
